## 文法・自然さフィードバック 📝

- "to take care of new comer" → **to take care of a newcomer**（冠詞 a + 一語で newcomer）
- "I was supposed not to be busy" → **I wasn't supposed to be busy**（not の位置）
- "CSAM set the meeting" → **CSAM set up a meeting**（set up + 冠詞）
- "I had a scoping meeging" → **I had a scoping meeting**（スペル）
- "there was a room for improvement" → **there was room for improvement**（a 不要、不可算）
- "In the eveneng" → **In the evening**（スペル）
- "I was not to end up all talk" → **I didn't want to end up being all talk**（意図が明確に）
- "try to feel the way out" → **try to feel my way out** / **find a way out**（所有格 my が必要、または find を使う）

## 良かった点 🌟

- テストで × だった **as good as it's going to get**（#258）と **bang one's head against the wall**（#307）を日記で使えたのは素晴らしい！実際の文脈で使うと記憶に残りやすい
- **have a whale of a time** と **heated discussion** も自然に使えている
- 1つの日記に7つもマスターリストのフレーズを盛り込めている！

